      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW MITCH (8) filled the minor money two on end before breaking through for a deserved win last time, scoring at Warrnambool over 390m (22.71). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from six attempts. Can make it two on the bounce. HAPPY BUDDHA (3) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (25.04) in a Grade 5 at Bendigo latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Expected to bounce back to best. HECTIC HARRY (1) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 6 lengths into third (23.02) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Will give a great sight again. JUSTIFIED JIM (2) has top-three aspirations after placing last time.",
